.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, classical, country, indie, punk, soul
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: december, august, november, october, march, may
1. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of soul##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the fan of blues##1
3. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of country is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
5. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
6. the fan of punk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
8. the person who's birthday is in november is the fan of indie##1
9. the fan of country is the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Music-Genre   | indie   | soul   | punk      | classical | blues  | country   |
| Birthday   | november | may | december | august   | march | october |

