.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, classical, country, disco, dubstep, indie
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, dunhill, baccarat, pall-mall, oliveros, alhambra
1. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the fan of country is on the far left##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
4. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
5. the alhambra-smoker is the fan of disco##1
6. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
7. the fan of dubstep is on the far right##1
8. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| Music-Genre   | country  | disco | blues      | classical  | indie | dubstep |
| Cigar     | bluemaster | alhambra  | oliveros | baccarat | pall-mall  | dunhill    |

