.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
There 6 different types of food: raspberry, carrot, grapefruit, pomegranate, pepper, lettuce
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: classical, country, disco, electronic, house, techno
 1. the fan of disco is the person eating raspberry##1
 2. the person eating carrot is on the left of the fan of country##1
 3. the fan of house is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
 4. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 5. the fan of classical is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
 6. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 7. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
 8. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 9. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
10. the person eating pomegranate is the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Food         | pomegranate | lettuce | raspberry | pepper | carrot | grapefruit  |
| Music-Genre   | techno  | electronic  | disco  | classical | house      | country |

