.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-6::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, zinnia, balloon-flower, marigold, aconite, poppy
There are 6 different nationalities: american, australian, brazilian, chinese, german, mexican
1. the mexican is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
2. the chinese is on the left of the american##1
3. the chinese is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
4. the australian is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
5. the german is the person who growspoppy##1
6. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the brazilian##1
7. the american is on the far right##1
8. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
9. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Flower   | poppy    | balloon-flower    | amaryllis | aconite     | zinnia   | marigold     |
| Nationality   | german | australian | mexican | brazilian | chinese | american |

