.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-7::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, prince, aristoff, vegafina, blend, alhambra
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, motorbike, roller, ship, snowmobile, trike
1. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
4. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the vegafina-smoker is the person driving the trike##1
6. the aristoff-smoker is the person driving the roller##1
7. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
8. the prince-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |   3   |     4      |   5   |     6      |
| Cigar         | prince       | alhambra     | vegafina | aristoff | blend | davidoff |
| Transport   | motorbike | snowmobile | trike | roller     | bike  | ship       |

