.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-8::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, tea, sprite
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, ice-hockey, rugby, volleyball, weightlifting
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is the person drinking sprite##1
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| Beverage   | sprite | coffee  | tea     | hot-chocolate    | almond-milk  | iced-tea          |
| Sport         | golf  | biathlon | ice-hockey | volleyball | rugby | weightlifting |

