.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-9::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, juice, soy-milk, sprite, tea
There are 6 different favourite colors: orange, ivory, red, apricot, yellow, blood-red
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
4. the person who likes blood-red is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
8. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |    3     |   4    |       5       |     6      |
| Beverage    | sprite | iced-tea | soy-milk | tea    | hot-chocolate | juice      |
| Color   | red   | orange     | ivory      | yellow | blood-red           | apricot |

