.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-10::.
There 6 different types of food: broccoli, cranberry, kiwi, onion, peach, peas
City: hannover, london, berlin, new-york, venice, edinburgh
1. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to london is the person eating cranberry##1
4. the person eating onion is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
5. the person traveling to new-york is on the far right##1
6. the person eating cranberry is on the far left##1
7. the person eating peas is the person traveling to hannover##1
8. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
9. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Food          | cranberry | peas   | peach  | kiwi    | onion  | broccoli |
| City   | london   | hannover | edinburgh | venice | berlin | new-york |

