.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-11::.
There 6 different types of food: cranberry, pear, asparagus, broccoli, raspberry, pineapple
The people have 6 different jobs:  coach, fisherman, librarian, manager, pilot, writer
1. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
2. the coach is on the right of the person eating pear##1
3. the person eating pineapple is on the far left##1
4. the librarian is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
5. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
6. the fisherman is on the far right##1
7. the person eating cranberry is the manager##1
8. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating pear##1
9. the pilot is on the left of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |   3   |      4      |    5     |     6     |
| Food   | pineapple    | cranberry     | asparagus | pear | broccoli | raspberry   |
| Job        | writer | manager | pilot | librarian   | coach    | fisherman |

