7. the french is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
8. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the spanish##1
9. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |    5    |    6    |
