The people prefer 6 different types of sport: handball, lacrosse, parkour, skateboarding, skiing, swimming
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who likes emerald##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is the person who likes blood-red##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
6. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who likes white##1
8. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3     |       4       |       5       |    6     |
