.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-17::.
6 different pets are kept: cat, goat, hamster, rat, snake, turtle
The people use 6 different means of transport: bus, scooter, boat, airplane, taxi, roller
1. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the rat is the person driving the bus##1
5. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
7. the person driving the boat is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
8. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
9. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |    3     |    4     |    5    |       6       |
| Pet     | snake  | rat       | turtle   | cat      | hamster | goat          |
| Transport   | taxi | bus | boat | scooter | airplane | roller |

