.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-20::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: country, funk, house, metal, rock, salsa
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: daisy, rose, begonia, balloon-flower, bellflower, dahlia
1. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of funk##1
3. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of house##1
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the fan of metal##1
5. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
6. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
7. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
8. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
9. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |     3      |   4    |   5   |     6      |
| Music-Genre   | funk | salsa     | rock       | house  | metal | country    |
| Flower     | dahlia  | daisy | rose | balloon-flower | bellflower  | begonia |

 